title: System of a down songs in 8-Bit (Nesmerize)
description:
This is a collection of all the 8-Bit versions of System of a Down songs.

I have called the album Nes-merize and Photoshopped a cover for it myself :) 

In the folder are 42 songs.

I created them by downloading them from youtube using YTD and then converting them to audio
using AVS Audio Converter

All songs are named and labeled with their album (Nesmerize) and artist (System of a Down (8-Bit))

Please enjoy and seed so more people can enjoy these awesome renditions of some great songs :)

This is my first torrent so please don't be too harsh
